b70a64","tid":152703,"uid":13465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"係香港點食大陸妹 d淫底有無得睇"},{"pid":"d43b90faa15e5b4fcbe58dd1efa57d890d9c28d3","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認同，大陸妹其實好多都好撚正，尤其有啲錢種。<br />\n父母一孩，獨女，你搞得好，成副身家都係你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我啲朋友話食咗之後你嗌分手大把手尾你跟，所以機本上你唔嗌得分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔需要自己嗌分手<br />\n如果真係一齊左 又想分手 咪對佢閪啲囉<br />\n愛理不理 令佢覺得自己貼錢買難受<br />\n到時佢就會走"},{"pid":"f3f287040d619989276b47bbc621ba48b93031cf","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主英國讀緊書？</blockquote><br />\n讀完啦 搵左成年工都未搵到"},{"pid":"337d5f1a0655677cf8b7632e035bd993da1a741e","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係食大陸妹仲可以大大聲講出黎，正皮你既勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食大陸妹 冇乜問題<br />\n本人唔太中意大陸妹既性格<br />\n所以要代佢老豆老母床上教訓佢"},{"pid":"bce1fa182c18c17787a005cc58d047ac52860f4f","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸妹叫床會講乜？</blockquote><br />\n佢地會叫 不要停～ 快點～ 呀～"},{"pid":"d6d7eac7d370a3f7b7e38de32f3e08f2a8c6b594","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間大學識？</blockquote><br />\n唔講邊間啦 我係倫敦讀"},{"pid":"b08a21c7f40b180d242ef041a8fe400f9702a178","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸妹係方便易屌，但係樓豬都唔駛食咁多餐快餐掛，對身體唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺身體差左<br />\n屌大陸妹好似比佢地吸乾咁"},{"pid":"0128ec8a178ebc9ef189ab5a26f775b3764f7df3","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁仲有果5%呢?</blockquote><br />\n香港人"},{"pid":"fa847c75eaf5923cee923c992f2aabe33ee5ad98","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有病未?</blockquote><br />\n我好健康 希望唔會有病"},{"pid":"cc9af7e9812ebafaf14ae0f0e0897c46887351e9","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15 個入面幾多個有豬？ 同埋佢地平均幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n大陸妹冇豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地隻豬一早比人食左<br />\n佢地平均20歲"},{"pid":"bda6f78ac51534c9ef1a8157270c8934c816c495","tid":152703,"uid":76284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"好似我個frd<br />\n狂食大陸妹🙈🙈🙈"},{"pid":"1036523944772667472ebb5b539008d53f5b3927","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係要好靚仔或身材好fit</blockquote><br />\n1. 屋企有錢<br />\n2. 靚仔 個樣岩佢地口味<br />\n3. 身材好 有哂腹肌咁樣<br />\n是但中一樣都夠"},{"pid":"d594f1e28d46cd6e6673a0fc651be725b7b27dd9","tid":152703,"uid":79814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺香港有冇食？</blockquote><br />\n香港都有 但小<br />\n離開左香港好多年 冇哂朋友<br />\n食都係用Skout黎搵女屌"},{"pid":"83183d953f7c3159cafc6f8ad32cd4d2bfcd2996","tid":152703,"uid":53011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"我諗香港班廢中地盤佬都食過好多大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2c2b9dae8a065f4a016ca310f4e54fd9e89f58","tid":152703,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"大陸妹多數大波<